title: PLAZA / WORKING CLASS WOMAN barks
description: What it says on the box.

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Woman: ""Not sure about this one...""
Working Class Woman: ""Wait... is this where he fakes his..."
dialogueTree.english: "Wait... is this where he fakes his own death?"
dialogueTree.polish: „Zaraz... To w tej części pozoruje swoją śmierć?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Момант... Дык у гэтай частцы ён імітуе сваю смерць?»

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Woman: ""Think I read this one already.""
Working Class Woman: ""Oh... it's a prequel?""
Working Class Woman: ""So melodramatic. Victor would hate..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Jakie to melodramatyczne. Victorowi by się nie spodobało”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Якое гэта меладраматычнае. Віктару б не спадабалася».

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Woman: ""I really should get this. For myse..."
dialogueTree.english: "I really should get this. For myself."

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Woman: ""It must be true, if it's in a book.""
dialogueTree.english: "It must be true, if it's in a book."
dialogueTree.polish: „To musi być prawda, skoro napisali o tym w książce”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Гэта павінна быць праўдай, бо пра гэта напісалі ў кнізе».

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Woman: ""Wonder if I could bring some of my..."
dialogueTree.english: "Wonder if I could bring some of my old books here?"
dialogueTree.polish: „Ciekawe, czy przyjęliby tu część moich starych książek”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Цікава, ці прынялі б тут частку маіх старых кніг».
